&lt;LI&gt;Applicable to 50, 63, 80, and 100mm bore sizes&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Foot bracket can be mounted on the rotary actuator bracket 90&#xb0; intervals&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

